Observations:¶


Following are the high correlations that we observe:

  • Mockito:

      • CBO vs [RFC,DIT,LCOM]
      • RFC vs [DIT]
  • Wildfly:
    • >50% :
      • CBO vs [RFC,DIT,LCOM]
      • RFC vs [DIT]
